# Calendar blocklist (OPTIONAL).
#
# Copy this file to "blocklist.txt" (same folder) and list the calendars you
# want to keep OFF-LIMITS — one name per line, exactly as shown by cal-list.sh.
# Lines starting with # and blank lines are ignored.
#
# Behaviour:
#   - File absent or empty  -> nothing is blocked; the skill works on EVERY
#                              calendar (the default).
#   - File lists names      -> those calendars are excluded from scans
#                              (events/search), and create/update/delete is
#                              REFUSED for them. Naming a blocked calendar
#                              explicitly also returns a clear error.
#
# Use this to fence off calendars an assistant shouldn't touch: a shared work
# calendar, a partner's calendar, subscribed holidays, Siri Suggestions, etc.
# Everything not listed stays fully accessible.
#
# Example:
# Work
# Holidays
# Birthdays
# Siri Suggestions
